issues.suggested_fix:
Make the solution's PersonController provide a no-argument constructor that matches how it is instantiated in H05E01ClientApplication, or change H05E01ClientApplication to call the parameterized constructor. Recommended fix: add a no-arg constructor to PersonController that delegates to the parameterized one with sensible defaults (for example baseUrl = "http://localhost:8080/" and a default timeout), e.g.

public PersonController() {
    this("http://localhost:8080/", Duration.ofSeconds(5));
}

This preserves the intended client behavior and matches the template/problem expectation.
